2/53639dbe-7864-4412-881e-1ee2e2ff2841/34dda0e0-c77e-11ed-851a-a5fe3e8b84ab/file-1lfhiezn3.png\" loading=\"lazy\" style=\"max-width:100%;height:auto;display:block;margin:0px auto;max-height:40vh\" alt=\"JEE Main 2023 (Online) 1st February Morning Shift Chemistry - Basics of Organic Chemistry Question 140 English Explanation 4\">",
